Baran贸wka  is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Frombork, within Braniewo County, Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship, in northern Poland. It lies approximately  south-east of Frombork,  south-west of Braniewo, and  north-west of the regional capital Olsztyn.
